title: New love: Cristiano Ronaldo dating 19-year-old Danish model
text:
22:40 CET New love: Cristiano Ronaldo dating 19-year-old Danish model - www.allsports.com.gh 
Another weekend, another attractive woman is linked to Real Madrid superstar Cristiano Ronaldo. 
Portuguese paper Correio Da Mahna have today jumped on reports from Scandinavia that Ronaldo has started dating 19-year-old Danish model Maja Darving. 
The story was first picked up by Denmark's BT, after the spotted that Maja Darving was at Real Madrid's Champions League match against Malmo last week. play
